        <property propertyId="38f94dd1-d5aa-41b8-b182-c0c42985d9dc" amount="160.0" unitId="7b75baf0-cbee-45e6-bf66-af119da06553">
          <name xml:lang="en">price</name>
          <unitName xml:lang="en">EUR2005</unitName>
          <comment xml:lang="en">Expert judgement (Urs Luginbühl, Swiss Sawmilling industry, personal communication in June 2014). Cross-reference; FAOSTAT (accessed 20140428). The price is calculated by using data on total world import quantity (m3) and import value (1000 USD), year 2005. 109432798 m3 of Sawnwood (C) - coniferous was imported in the world in 2005. The import value was 22249842000 USD. The calculated price is thus (22249842000/109432798=203*0.8=) 164 Euro.</comment>
        </property>
